                             @{b}@{u} WEAPONS GALORE @{ub}@{uu}




     1-Pistol

       It is the weapon you start each mission with.
       Besides the machine gun and the secret weapon,it is the only weapon
       which can be shot while jumping.

       RANGE: medium
       POWER: medium
       RELOAD TIME:medium

     2-Machine gun

       Fast and flexible.As well as the pistol and the secret weapon,it can
       be shot in mid-air.It is slighty less powerful than the pistol,but
       it more than makes up with is fast fire rate.

       RANGE:short
       POWER:low
       RELOAD TIME:low

     3-Shotgun

       One of Charly's personal favourites,the shotgun is 3 times more
       powerful than the pistol.It's slighty sluggish between shoots.

       RANGE:medium-long
       POWER:medium-high
       RELOAD TIME:medium-high

     4-Missile Launcher

       A devastating weapon,it's only drawback being the high reload time.

       RANGE:long
       POWER:high
       RELOAD TIME:high

     5-Flame-thrower:

       Charly's other fave weapon.It is the only weapon in the whole game
       that can be shoot whilst walking.A bit bulky,though.

       RANGE:medium
       POWER:high
       RELOAD TIME:very low

     6-Secret Weapon:

       The most powerful weapon in the game.It is usually very well hidden.
       Can be shoot while jumping,too.

       RANGE:long
       POWER:very high
       RELOAD TIME:medium


     Bear in mind that when you are wielding a weapon,you lose energy if an
     enemy touches it.On the other hand,big weapons can be used to collect
     items while jumping,by touching them (especially the flame-thrower).
     Note that in Mission 3,you'll come across two special weapons,which fit
     in well with the theme of the level...



